Ensure to work in a Grid system as it allows you to bulid responsive web pages. container>row>cols
<hr> Used to have a horizontal rule.
We can a make a button that can have href
It can be done using <a href btn btn-primary>Sign</a>

bg-dark, bg-light, text-light, text-dark etc can also be there

To make a better displaying jumborton use
<div class="container">(this adds margin both to the left and right)
  <div class="jumborton">
     <h1 class="display-4">
       Hello World!!
     </h1>
     <p class="lead"> Hope you are doing well. Will see you next time
     </p>
     <a class="btn btn-danger btn-lg" href="#">Click Me</a>
  </div>
</div>

<h3 class="text-primary display-4"> I have a primary color </div>
<button>
  <button class="btn btn-lg btn-danger"> DANGER BUTTON</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-info btn-lg">OUTLINE BUTTON</button>
        <h1> Big Text<small class="text-muted">make me muted</small></h1>
        <p class="bg-dark text-white text-center"> Dark backround white text and aligned centre</p>
        <button class="btn btn-link">This button looks like a Link</button>

Colors can be applied to button,text,border by using text-primary,btn btn-primary,border border-primary

Shadow can also be given as shadow-lg,shadow,shadow-sm
Margin and Padding are also essential for the designing of a web page.
mt-5 mb-5 mr-5 ml-9 mx-4 my-3 similar is the scenario for padding u can add it pt,pr,pl,pb,px,py
You can also make the margin responsive by adding things like this 
m-3 m-md-5 It means margin will be 3 for small devices and it will be 5 or greater for md or bigger than that devices

<small class="text-muted>Password must be at least 8 characters </small> It will display small and Opaque text.

PREPARATION OF FORM USING BOOTSTRAP
<form>
<div class="formgroup>
<label for="imagefile">Upload File </label>
<input type="file" class="form-control-file" id="imagefile">
// form-control-file is a special type of form-control which enhances the view.
</div>
</form>












